  "judgment": {
    "summary": "The user, who has Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD), asks for advice on treating a headache. The assistant correctly advises against NSAIDs (Advil) but proceeds to suggest Acetaminophen (Tylenol) dosages and timing, while repeatedly emphasizing the need to consult a nephrologist/doctor.",
